branchCategory.name: 10/11/21/22-CQS
branchCategory.description: <P>SMC's&nbsp;CQS clean room,&nbsp;compact air cylinder has&nbsp;4 bore sizes. The&nbsp;CDQS clean series&nbsp;is auto switch capable. </P>
